        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;"><strong>2. Forget gate </strong>— discover what details to be discarded from the block. It is decided by the <strong>sigmoid function. </strong>it looks at the previous state(<strong>ht-1</strong>) and the content input(<strong>Xt</strong>) and outputs a number between <strong>0(</strong><em>omit this</em>)and <strong>1(</strong><em>keep this</em><strong>)</strong>for each number in the cell state <strong>Ct−1</strong>.</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="image3 cid-tt612oXwA9" id="image3-5" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
